<figureCitation box="[681,752,1212,1234]" captionStart="FIGURES 19 – 26" captionStartId="6.[151,264,1260,1283]" captionTargetBox="[158,1430,200,1229]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[150,1436,193,1239]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 19 – 26. Pronotum: 19. Macrolygistopterus succinctus; 20. M. quadricostatus; 21. M. caeruleus; 22. M. germaini; 23. M. grandjeani; 24. M. simoni; 25. M. subparallelus; 26. M. testaceirostris. Scale bar 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/271309/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="335">
